  "title": "Store Packer",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>MNC Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $2200 - $2400 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Jurong East</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: Monday to Friday (8.30am to 5.30pm), Alternate Saturday (8.30am\nto 12.30am)</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Pick items from warehouse shelves according to order specifications</li><li>Prepare items for shipment by checking quality, securely wrapping, and boxing products</li><li>Checking their quality, securely wrapping and boxing them</li><li>Receive, store, pack, and unpack goods</li><li>Deliver goods from suppliers when required</li><li>Load and unload vehicles/trucks</li><li>Carry and move goods as part of daily operation</li><li>Assist with stock counts when required</li><li>Maintain regular housekeeping standards in the warehouse</li><li>Other ad hoc duties as assigned </li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Possess minimum GCE ‘N’ Level qualification or above with 1-2 years relevant experience</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
